<br>
But yes it globally widen the gap even more between the skald and the vast majority of the hybrid classes , and of course tanks. Even the 2handed hybrids (LW champions and the like) with 2.0 spec have more &quot;leftover points&quot; to put into parry.<br>
<br>
It gives us a little advantage above minstrels and assassin classes, but not worth imho the loss of even more fighting abilities against practically every other melee class out there.<br>
<br>
